msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/01"
msgid ""
"Soldaten! The Canadians are not too far away from here and we are the only "
"ones standing in their way to Walcheren."
msgstr ""
"¡Soldados! Los canadienses no están muy lejos de aquí y somos los únicos que "
"se interponen en su camino hacia Walcheren."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/02"
msgid ""
"Even the flooded fields are not stopping them... We are the first line of "
"defence of Woensdrecht and Hoogerheide and we need to hold our current "
"positions as long as possible to have time to prepare our main defences on "
"the higher ground."
msgstr ""
"Ni siquiera los campos inundados los detienen... Somos la primera línea de "
"defensa de Woensdrecht y Hoogerheide y debemos mantener nuestras posiciones "
"actuales el mayor tiempo posible para tener tiempo de preparar nuestras "
"defensas principales en las zonas más elevadas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/03"
msgid ""
"Do not allow the enemy to breach our line. Our main defences are not ready "
"yet. Hold your positions along the roads going from East to West."
msgstr ""
"No permitas que el enemigo rompa nuestras líneas. Nuestras defensas "
"principales aún no están listas. Mantén tus posiciones a lo largo de las "
"carreteras que van de este a oeste."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/04"
msgid ""
"The Canadians are surely going to bring a lot of armor, you can find anti-"
"tank and anti-personnel mines in the engineering trucks. Try to lay as many "
"as possible on the roads going from South to North."
msgstr ""
"Los canadienses seguramente traerán mucho armamento, puedes encontrar minas "
"antitanque y antipersonales en los camiones de ingeniería. Intenta colocar "
"tantas como puedas en las carreteras que van de sur a norte."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/05"
msgid "Good job. That should help us delay them."
msgstr "Buen trabajo. Eso debería ayudarnos a retrasarlos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/06"
msgid "Enemy artillery! Take cover!"
msgstr "¡Artillería enemiga! ¡A cubierto!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/07"
msgid "They are coming on the left flank!"
msgstr "¡Vienen por el flanco izquierdo!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/08"
msgid ""
"Our scouts are predicting we still have a couple of minutes before the enemy "
"arrives. Use this time wisely. Strengthen our weak points and make sure we "
"have anti-tank weapons pointing at every road."
msgstr ""
"Nuestros exploradores predicen que aún quedan un par de minutos antes de que "
"llegue el enemigo. Aprovecha este tiempo sabiamente. Refuerza nuestros "
"puntos débiles y asegúrate de que tenemos armas antitanque apuntando a todas "
"las carreteras."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/09"
msgid ""
"They are taking a beating on the left flank but seems like they are starting "
"a new attack on the right flank!"
msgstr ""
"Están recibiendo una paliza en el flanco izquierdo, ¡pero parece que están "
"iniciando un nuevo ataque en el flanco derecho!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/10"
msgid ""
"Take a look inside the boxes, you should find some grenades, explosives and "
"panzerfausts there."
msgstr ""
"Echa un vistazo dentro de las cajas, deberías encontrar algunas granadas, "
"explosivos y panzerfausts."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/11"
msgid "They are deploying more troops on both flanks!"
msgstr "¡Están desplegando más tropas en ambos flancos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/12"
msgid ""
"We cannot hold the first line for much longer, or we'll be overrun. Our guns "
"on the second line should be deployed already. Move your men back to "
"strengthen the main defences."
msgstr ""
"No podemos mantener la primera línea mucho más tiempo, o nos invadirán. "
"Nuestras armas de la segunda línea ya deberían estar desplegadas. Haz que "
"tus hombres retrocedan para reforzar las defensas principales."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/13"
msgid ""
"We need to hold three strategic positions that ensure the Canadians can't "
"break through. We have a couple of 8,8 cm guns and 10,5 cm howitzers, make "
"use of them."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos que mantener tres posiciones estratégicas que impidan el avance de "
"los canadienses. Tenemos un par de cañones de 8,8 cm y obuses de 10,5 cm, "
"utilícenlos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/14"
msgid ""
"Enemy artillery barrage!! They likely know where our positions are now so "
"take cover!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡Fuego de artillería enemigo!! Probablemente ya saben dónde estamos, ¡así "
"que poneros a cubierto!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/15"
msgid "Finally! Our reinforcements are here!"
msgstr "¡Por fin! ¡Han llegado los refuerzos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/16"
msgid ""
"We cannot afford losing any more ground! Our mission is over, we are on the "
"verge of ending up in another pocket. Holding Woensdrecht is impossible, now "
"we have to fight for our lives."
msgstr ""
"¡No podemos permitirnos perder más terreno! Nuestra misión ha terminado, "
"estamos a punto de acabar en otro bolsillo. Mantener Woensdrecht es "
"imposible, ahora tenemos que luchar por nuestras vidas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_officer/17"
msgid ""
"The situation is falling apart quickly. The Allies are gaining ground. We "
"must hold our positions for at least five more minutes so our command can "
"reposition."
msgstr ""
"La situación se está deteriorando rápidamente. Los aliados están ganando "
"terreno. Debemos mantener nuestras posiciones durante al menos cinco minutos "
"más para que nuestro mando pueda reorganizarse."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/01"
msgid ""
"It never stops raining here. The mud is worse than in the East. At least "
"there it froze."
msgstr ""
"Aquí nunca deja de llover. El barro es peor que en el este. Al menos allí se "
"congelaba."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/02"
msgid ""
"They keep coming. Artillery, infantry and tanks. How much longer can we hold "
"them back?"
msgstr ""
"Siguen llegando. Artillería, infantería y tanques. ¿Cuánto tiempo más "
"podremos contenerlos?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/03"
msgid ""
"Do you believe that still matters? The Allies already have France. They have "
"supplies, fuel... everything. Their logistics are much better than ours..."
msgstr ""
"¿Crees que eso sigue siendo importante? Los aliados ya tienen Francia. "
"Tienen suministros, combustible... todo. Tu logística es mucho mejor que la "
"nuestra..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/04"
msgid ""
"Survive… for what? Another pocket? Another retreat? Haven't we been through "
"enough of that recently?"
msgstr ""
"¿Sobrevivir... para qué? ¿Para otro bolsillo? ¿Para otra retirada? ¿No hemos "
"pasado ya por suficiente últimamente?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/05"
msgid ""
"Clear! That must have been a resistance hideout. Let's see what else they've "
"been hiding here."
msgstr ""
"¡Despejado! Debía de ser un escondite de la resistencia. Veamos qué más han "
"estado escondiendo aquí."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/06"
msgid "A damaged howitzer? Why hasn't anyone repaired it yet?"
msgstr "¿Un obús dañado? ¿Por qué nadie lo ha reparado todavía?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier1/07"
msgid "Just like new! Now let's make use of it."
msgstr "¡Como nuevo! Ahora vamos a darle uso."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/01"
msgid ""
"Don’t complain. Mud means tanks get stuck. And we need every advantage "
"against those Canadians."
msgstr ""
"No te quejéis. El barro hace que los tanques se atasquen. Y necesitamos "
"todas las ventajas posibles contra esos canadienses."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/02"
msgid ""
"Until we’re ordered otherwise. That’s how it works. If we fail Walcheren "
"will be open to the Allies and it’s the key to the Scheldt. As long as we "
"remain here, Antwerp is useless to them"
msgstr ""
"Hasta que se nos ordene lo contrario. Así es como funciona. Si fracasamos, "
"Walcheren quedará abierta a los aliados y será la clave del Escalda. "
"Mientras permanezcamos aquí, Amberes les será inútil."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/03"
msgid ""
"Better to keep your eyes on your section and your rifle ready than think of "
"such things. That’s how you survive."
msgstr ""
"Es mejor mantener la vista en tu sección y el rifle listo que pensar en esas "
"cosas. Así es como se sobrevive."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/04"
msgid ""
"You survive for the man next to you. For the chance that we see home again. "
"That’s enough for me..."
msgstr ""
"Sobrevives por el hombre que tienes al lado. Por la posibilidad de volver a "
"ver tu hogar. Eso es suficiente para mí..."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/05"
msgid "Wait! I see someone with a weapon inside that house!"
msgstr "¡Espera! ¡Veo a alguien con un arma dentro de esa casa!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/narrator_soldier2/06"
msgid ""
"Let's take a few repairs kits and try to put this gun back in action. We "
"will need it!"
msgstr ""
"Cojamos unos cuantos kits de reparación e intentemos volver a poner esta "
"pistola en funcionamiento. ¡La vamos a necesitar!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/reinforcement/"
"skip_preparation"
msgid "Skip preparation"
msgstr "Saltar preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task01"
msgid "Prepare to defend the first line"
msgstr "Prepárate para defender la primera línea."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task02"
msgid "Hold the first line until the main defences are ready"
msgstr ""
"Mantén la primera línea hasta que las defensas principales estén listas."

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task03"
msgid "Hold the artillery hill! (hold at least 2 out of 3 zones)"
msgstr "¡Mantén la colina de artillería! (mantén al menos 2 de las 3 zonas)"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task04"
msgid "Hold the windmill hill! (hold at least 2 out of 3 zones)"
msgstr "¡Defended la colina del molino! (mantened al menos 2 de las 3 zonas)"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task05"
msgid "Hold the railroad line! (hold at least 2 out of 3 zones)"
msgstr "¡Mantén la línea ferroviaria! (mantén al menos 2 de las 3 zonas)"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task06"
msgid "Hold your ground! (hold at least 2 out of 3 zones)"
msgstr "¡Mantén tu posición! (mantén al menos 2 de las 3 zonas)"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task_secret01"
msgid "Secret objective #1: Lay at least 100 mines"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 1: Colocar al menos 100 minas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/"
"task_secret01_hidden"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task_secret02"
msgid "Secret objective #2: Find the Dutch resistance hideout"
msgstr ""
"Objetivo secreto n.º 2: Encontrar el escondite de la resistencia holandesa."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/"
"task_secret02_hidden"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 2"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/task_secret03"
msgid "Secret objective #3: Repair the damaged howitzer"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 3: Reparar el obús dañado."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/tasks/"
"task_secret03_hidden"
msgid "Secret objective #3"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto n.º 3"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/timer/defend"
msgid "Hold your ground for at least:"
msgstr "Mantén tu posición durante al menos:"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/timer/preparation"
msgid "Time before the enemy attack"
msgstr "Tiempo antes del ataque enemigo"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/name"
msgid "The Black Friday"
msgstr "El Viernes Negro"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/name_big"
msgid "The Black Friday"
msgstr "El Viernes Negro"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"You have completed all mission objectives but this was a battle we couldn't "
"win. With our determination we managed to slow down the Canadian attack just "
"enough to regroup our forces and avoid even heavier losses."
msgstr ""
"Has completado todos los objetivos de la misión, pero esta era una batalla "
"que no podíamos ganar. Con nuestra determinación, logramos ralentizar el "
"ataque canadiense lo suficiente como para reagrupar nuestras fuerzas y "
"evitar pérdidas aún mayores."


msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Was that really all you could do? The Allies are now storming Walcheren "
"peninsula, which means the harbor of Antwerp will be open to them very soon. "
"You should organise a last ditch effort to undo this loss!"
msgstr ""
"¿Era eso realmente todo lo que podías hacer? Los aliados están ahora "
"invadiendo la península de Walcheren, lo que significa que el puerto de "
"Amberes estará abierto para ellos muy pronto. ¡Deberías organizar un último "
"esfuerzo para revertir esta pérdida!"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/date"
msgid "October 10th, 1944 · Woensdrecht, North-Brabant, Netherlands"
msgstr ""
"10 de octubre de 1944 · Woensdrecht, Brabante Septentrional, Países Bajos"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/place"
msgid "Kampfgruppe Chill"
msgstr "Kampfgruppe Chill"

msgctxt "mission/single/051-ger_finesthour/1944_10_woensdrecht/story"
msgid ""
"The Allies are still unable to use the harbor of Antwerp, and all of their "
"supplies have to be brought in from Normandy by truck. \n"
"\n"
" For this reason, the Canadians have started advancing in the direction of "
"Woensdrecht today. They intend to gain access to the Zuid-Beveland peninsula "
"and the Scheldt estuary. \n"
"\n"
" You have been stationed at Hoogerheide, where you will stop them from "
"breaking through to the peninsula. The stakes could not be higher!"
msgstr ""
"Los aliados siguen sin poder utilizar el puerto de Amberes, y todos tus "
"suministros tienen que ser transportados desde Normandía en camión. Por este "
"motivo, los canadienses han comenzado hoy a avanzar en dirección a "
"Woensdrecht. Su intención es acceder a la península de Zuid-Beveland y al "
"estuario del Escalda. \n"
"\n"
" Tú has sido destinado a Hoogerheide, donde impedirás que atraviesen la "
"península. ¡Lo que está en juego no podría ser más importante!"
